We are seeking experienced and passionate environment artist for full time positions. This position must be proficient in 3DS Max and Unreal Engine 3. Ideal candidates will have shipped titles under their belt and be familiar with the game development process. Additionally artists should have a strong understanding of technical implications of art in game engines and a firm understanding of best practices in game development.</p>
<p>
<strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Develop high quality and efficient art to populate levels.</li>
<li>
Work with the Art Lead to ensure that the game&rsquo;s environments have a unified and consistent look.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Passionate, capable, driven worker who enjoys creating and playing games.</li>
<li>
Experience working in Unreal Engine 3.</li>
<li>
Strong knowledge of 3DS Max (or similar suite) and Adobe Photoshop.</li>
<li>
Experience with Zbrush or Mudbox is a plus.</li>
<li>
Technical understanding of art and it&rsquo;s impact on the game engine 2+ years of industry(or relevant) experience or a strong portfolio.</li>
<li>
Must be a US citizen.</li>
</ul>
