			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Zombie Studios Consumer Games Division is currently seeking an experienced and passionate animator for a full time position. Ideal candidates are highly skilled in Motion Builder as well as Maya and or Max. Experience working with the Unreal Engine 3 is a plus, as is experience working with mo-cap data. Candidates should have shipped titles for the PC, Xbox360 and/or PS3. Kinect experience is an additional plus.</p>
<p>
<strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Develop high quality animations through key framing and motion capture data.</li>
<li>
Work with character artists and riggers to ensure that animations work properly for all models.</li>
<li>
Work with engineers to ensure that animations function as intended and are hooked up properly in game.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
2+ years of industry experience and a strong portfolio.</li>
<li>
Passionate, skilled, and driven team player who enjoys creating and playing games and working in a team environment.</li>
<li>
Skilled with Maya (or 3DS Max Character Studio) and Motion Builder.</li>
<li>
Experience working in Unreal Engine 3.</li>
<li>
Technical understanding of animations and their impact on the game.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
