<li>
Unreal Engine 3 experience with strong knowledge of Unreal Script</li>
<li>
Understanding of game development lifecycle and process</li>
<li>
Strong applied C++ programming experience</li>
<li>
Excellent debugging skills, including the creation and use of tools to debug networking functionality.</li>
<li>
Must have excellent organization and communication skills</li>
<li>
Passion for FPS and Action Games</li>
</ul>
